features: 【6 Set Packing Cubes Includes】: 3 Packing Cubes (L, M, S), 1 Laundry Bag, 1 Toiletry bag. This Travel Luggage Organizers Set fit for 24’/25’ suitcase.

【Packing Cubes Size】: Large( 16.5" x 12.6" x 4.73") Medium (13.39" x 11" x 4.73") Small (12.6” x 9.1” x 4.73") Underwear Bag (11.02” x 7.88” x 4.73" ) Toiletry Bag (14.17” x 6.3”) Laundry Bag (14.17” x 10.63”) – Everything well packed in 6 Set Packing Cubes.

【High Quality Travel Luggage Organizers】: Made of high-quality waterproof NYLON. Mesh top panel for easy identification of contents and well separate different clothes as you like. Strong two sides zippers and double stitched layers make Adwaita Packing Cubes become your most valued and reliable travel buddy.
【Packing Cubes for easy storage】: After using it, it can be folded into the toiletry bag and only takes small room in your wardrobe to wait for the next travel.

【Various Uses of Luggage Packing Organizers】: Adwaita packing cubes can be a good accompany of your FAMILY breaks, BUSINESS travel, BACKPACKING, CAMPING, HIKING, RV, CRUISE holidays & SADDLEBAGS or HOME STORAGE. Each of them is with handles on the top and can be used separately as a hand carry luggage.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 19, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars YOU WILL BE SHOCKED!!!
reviews.reviewText: So, i got these because my family and i were traveling and i happened to come across a tiktok that raved about these. When it came in the mail i honestly was very weary and hesitant.. i was like "all my clothes are supposed to fit in here?!" BUT how it proved me so wrong and left my husband and i amazed.. lol THE AMOUNT OF CLOTHES THAT YOU CAN FIT!!! It is very light-weight, our bags were under the 50 pound limit, and it was such a convenience because we went to 3 different hotels! The ONLY downside was that it did rip a little on the side but i would still buy another in a heartbeat.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good packing cubes!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased these packing cubes for a trip and they've served their purpose quite well! The item comes in different sizes and as someone who does not pack lightly, I was able to fit my clothes in within these cubes. I love how these cubes keep my suitcase organized and it makes it easier for me to find my clothes, rather than rummage through them. There was an issue with the zipper for one of the packing cubes, but it wasn't a big deal, I was able to fix it. Pretty good packing cubes for a good price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Cute and work well!
reviews.reviewText: These are super cute and get the job done! I bought these to organize my suitcase for my trip to Europe and they worked well. The only downside is that they don’t feel super high quality, so if you’re using them all the time they may not hold up. I’ve only used them a few times though and I’ve had no problems. Overall, I recommend these if you’re looking for packing cubes that are cute and affordable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 15, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great buy for travelers
reviews.reviewText: I like organizing my clothes and toiletries when I travel. This product is not only functional but the quality is very good. I actually use it for 2 of my luggage’s . The sizes makes sense and the product is made with good materials.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Loved these packing cubes! Saved a ton a room in my suite case. I gave it 4 stars because 1 of my zippers broke on day 2 just the circle off the zipper. I believe it could be fixed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Cute but cheap
reviews.reviewText: These packing cubes came in a nice assortment of sizes and functioned well for us, however, the quality is not the greatest. The plastic zippers on these are lightweight and the material is cheap. I prefer the Amazon packing cubes to these, by far.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars As pictured.. compact
reviews.reviewText: the quality and price ....and not bulky, very light and easy to pack... really good for organizing and for travel.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice for travel
reviews.reviewText: Haven’t had a chance to use yet but came highly recommended by a friend
These are excellent! See-through mesh, double zippers with loop pulls, excellent quality.
Love the concept of cubes but these were not sturdy. Broke almost instantly without packing too much into them.
I love the way it kept my clothes neat and organized. When opened at the custom they were shocked how easy it was for them. I also bout for my husband and my daughter. Great buy.

reviews.reviewTitle: I thought they were a bit bigger
reviews.reviewText: I found them a little useless really. I thought they would have been bigger. Cheap material. One of the clasps broke while I was packing my bathing suits it it. Cheap quality. Spend more for a better quality product
Bought for the second time as a gift great product
